snippet.title: 'The Librarian' Trailer. A short game by Octavi Navarro.
snippet.description:
Liz's library is threatened by the unknown. She must go investigate. She's the librarian, after all.  GET IT NOW! 
On itch.io:
https://octavinavarro.itch.io/the-librarian
On Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1364010/The_Librarian/ 
On GOG:
https://www.gog.com/en/game/the_librarian

I hope you enjoy it!! :)
